---
admin: true
guest: false
name: "Dash"
---

Without trimming, whitespace is preserved:
{{ if admin }}
  Welcome, admin!
{{ /if }}

With trimming on all tags:
{{- if admin -}}
  Welcome, admin!
{{- /if -}}

Trim on if/endif but not content:
{{- if admin }}
  Hello {{ name }}!
{{- /if -}}

If-else without trimming:
{{ if guest }}
  Guest view
{{ else }}
  Normal view
{{ /if }}

If-else with full trimming:
{{- if guest -}}
  Guest view
{{- else -}}
  Normal view
{{- /if -}}

Mixed trimming on else-if chain:
Start
{{- if guest -}}
Guest
{{- else if admin -}}
Admin
{{- else -}}
Unknown
{{- /if -}}
End

Inline if (no newlines):
[{{- if admin -}}yes{{- /if -}}]

False condition with trimming:
[{{- if guest -}}hidden{{- /if -}}]
